        <mj-text align="center" css-class="section_header" font-weight="bold">
          Marketing
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text>
          <ul>
            <li>Created and implemented digital marketing campaigns using Salesforce and Pardot</li>
            <li>Collaborated on creative direction</li>
            <li>Analyzed effectiveness of social media and e-mail campaigns</li>
            <li>Developed and deployed HTML emails, forms and splash pages</li>
            <li>Wrote and edited marketing copy</li>
          </ul>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-image src="https://benragsdalestuff.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/triangle-white.png"></mj-image>

      </mj-column>

      <mj-column css-class="webdev_div">
        <mj-image src="https://benragsdalestuff.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/triangle-3.png"></mj-image>
        <mj-text align="center" css-class="section_header" font-weight="bold">
          Web Development
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text align="left">
          <ul>
            <li>Developed eCommerce websites using Wordpress, PHP, JS, CSS</li>
            <li>Created custom taxonomies and rules in PHP </li>
            <li>Utilized Advanced Custom Fields in PHP to speed workflows</li>
            <li>Utilized SVGs and sprites to make the sites faster</li>
            <li>Tested websites for speed and accessibility</li>
            <li>Removed unneeded CSS, JS, PHP, and plugins</li>
          </ul>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-image src="https://benragsdalestuff.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/triangle-white.png"></mj-image>

      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
    <mj-section>
      <mj-column>
        <mj-image src="https://benragsdalestuff.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/triangle-3.png"></mj-image>
        <mj-button href="https://bennyrags.github.io/resume.html" target="_blank" css-class="button">
          Check Out my Resume!
        </mj-button>
      </mj-column>
